    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Housing built by a slow step-by-step process whereby building components are added or altered by owner-builders as money, time, or materials become available.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
